                            	     2: MERDA:
02:00001AB2 4D45524441204D45	     3:     DC.B    "MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA MERDA ",13,10,0
02:00001ABA 524441204D455244
